ass="t m0 x9 hd y1dc ffc fs3 fc0 sc1 ls55 ws0">（四） </div><div class="t m0 x44 hb y8a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">愿我目睹恶劣众，造罪遭受剧苦时， </div><div class="t m0 x44 hb y3a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">犹如值遇珍宝藏，以难得心爱惜之。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 y8c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">当见到恶劣众生因造罪业而遭受剧苦时，<span class="_ _a"></span>愿我犹如遇到</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
